Class BaseModulesFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rjrudin.marklogic.modulesloader.impl.BaseModulesFinder

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultModulesFinder, TestServerModulesFinder

    public abstract class BaseModulesFinder
extends java.lang.Object
implements ModulesFinder
    Abstract implementation that provides implementations for loading all the different kinds of modules, but doesn't actually implement findModules.
